{"tid":2267714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗官曱甴]警作供偷看「掌心雷」 六旬漢上訴襲警罪失敗即時收監","createTime":"2020-11-02T09:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T11:20:02.000Z","uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bf79f87539dd985b0d17be923c034c7bbd5635c4","tid":2267714,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:27:31.000Z","msg":"地盤工被控兩項襲警罪，早前審訊時，有作供警員被辯方發現將資料暗中寫於手掌上，但原審裁判官裁定所有警員證人誠實可靠，被告罪成判囚五星期。<br />\n<br />\n被告就定罪及刑期提上訴，今於高等法院審理。上訴方質疑兩名警員證供南轅北轍，互相矛盾，裁判官卻照樣接納。惟法官潘敏琦聽罷雙方陳詞後駁回上訴，稍後頒發理由，而保釋中的被告須即時收監。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曱甴鍾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhyOMKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhyOMKZ.jpg&h=19555664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n狗官潘敏琦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nn0CRV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nn0CRV.jpg&h=ddb793f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe850f0cb436e03f0316e76a370a7b1f3354b93c","tid":2267714,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xudNJsZ6dNk&amp;list=PLom-AMGF51O-Qy3yqseGud0IAmHPEEXnl&amp;index=9&amp;t=15s&amp;ab_channel=BBCNews%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxudNJsZ6dNk%26list%3DPLom-AMGF51O-Qy3yqseGud0IAmHPEEXnl%26index%3D9%26t%3D15s%26ab_channel%3DBBCNews%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=08ef8faa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xudNJsZ6dNk&amp;list=PLom-AMGF51O-Qy3yqseGud0IAmHPEEXnl&amp;index=9&amp;t=15s&amp;ab_channel=BBCNews%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87</a>"},{"pid":"ceb9a5e084ae1aedd88a7d47c8fd5b128a1adf94","tid":2267714,"uid":33099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"潘敏琦不嬲藍到爆炸"},{"pid":"d5708bd0d4a236c1170607531075f14e5bda6073","tid":2267